## üìÇ Repository Structure

```
scribe/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ scribe.py              # Main Scribe CLI tool (HTML output, GitHub repos)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ packrepo/              # FastPath algorithm library
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ library.py         # Public API (RepositoryPacker, ScribeConfig)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ fastpath/          # Core algorithms (v1-v5)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ packer/            # File selection and formatting
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ evaluator/         # Research evaluation framework
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ cli/fastpack.py    # Library CLI interface (text output, local repos)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ research/              # Research validation and analysis
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ eval/                  # Evaluation datasets and protocols
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ tests/                 # Comprehensive test suite
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ scripts/               # Automation and validation tools
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ docs/                  # Documentation and research papers
```

